rovider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="e77KqBXfb1"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/gossipy-vtuber-declares-victory-over-nijisanji-anycolor-the-company-didnt-reply-to-our-rebuttal/">八卦VTuber Nijisanji运营商ANYCOLOR称“胜利宣言”“公司不回复反驳”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“基于八卦的 VTuber Nijisanji 运营商 ANYCOLOR 宣布胜利” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/gossipy-vtuber-declares-victory-over-nijisanji-anycolor-the-company-didnt-reply-to-our-rebuttal/embed/#?secret=GDZrQirJ7R#?secret=e77KqBXfb1" data-secret="e77KqBXfb1" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>过去，劳伦因非法下载成人视频并发表有争议的言论而受到观众和粉丝的批评，认为这是不离不弃的指控 。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="LpxzXT68Mf"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-lauren-iroas-apologized-for-saying-hwabyuing-fabyotteiru-in-streaming/">VTuber Lauren Iroas 为直播时说“I&#39;m fabyo”而道歉</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Lauren Iroas 为在直播期间说“Fabyo”而道歉”— P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-lauren-iroas-apologized-for-saying-hwabyuing-fabyotteiru-in-streaming/embed/#?secret=QHTqjkskYI#?secret=LpxzXT68Mf" data-secret="LpxzXT68Mf" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="hwilq6476042cd1b86" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
