14299979781" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AJFCJaVhZ9h1pca6CUPLrDSRz8bQxhjKVChZkYp6Ev7Byn8e9zwFF2pW2fHYU4XdMgw4L-ohSZILAoQPOgjlcPdDO9Y8fMY0NZr3zo3vnjA3gMnwU0hxPwAPdfhiSRHVOMVmV8YtXN6nnbFAtGvzHk-SyNq-=w1097-h1410-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><p>公司于3月3日成立VTuber办公室“ <strong>FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION</strong> ”，并于3月10日宣布七位新艺人登场。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="8sOqbi2Wfh"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/reality-studios-establishes-vtuber-agency-first-stage-production-and-debuts-7-new-talents/">成立REALITY Studios VTuber办公室“FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION”7位新人登场</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“REALITY Studios VTuber 办公室“FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION”成立 7 位新人出道” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/reality-studios-establishes-vtuber-agency-first-stage-production-and-debuts-7-new-talents/embed/#?secret=vLL4fIIjJ9#?secret=8sOqbi2Wfh" data-secret="8sOqbi2Wfh" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@1stpro_official" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">第一阶段生产</a>/<a href="https://twitter.com/1stpro_official" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">第一阶段生产</a>/<a href="https://firststage-pro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">第一阶段生产</a></p><cite>YouTube/Twitter/REALITY Studios</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp 管理代表“No.2（临时）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙 VTuber 信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-first-stage-production-announces-commencement-of-legal-action-against-slander-etc/">VTuber 办公室 FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION 宣布开始对诽谤等采取法律行动。</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-first-stage-production-announ