記されているデータが存在する場合があります。予めご了承下さい。 </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="535W8A7D4g"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-lucid-multimedia-announces-10-day-suspention-of-vtuber-roza-coatl/">VTuber事務所 lucid Multimedia 所属VTuber ローザ・コアトル (Roza Coatl) の活動停止を発表</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber事務所 lucid Multimedia 所属VTuber ローザ・コアトル (Roza Coatl) の活動停止を発表&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-lucid-multimedia-announces-10-day-suspention-of-vtuber-roza-coatl/embed/#?secret=FdtY8tOL4P#?secret=535W8A7D4g" data-secret="535W8A7D4g" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="6BBrkGXx3U"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/myholotv-vtuber-woozie-wannai-11-day-hiatus/">MyHolo TV 所属VTuber 湾内ウージ (Woozie Wannai) 活動を11日間休止</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;MyHolo TV 所属VTuber 湾内ウージ (Woozie Wannai) 活動を11日間休止&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/myholotv-vtuber-woozie-wannai-11-day-hiatus/embed/#?secret=kjtnBQOdGY#?secret=6BBrkGXx3U" data-secret="6BBrkGXx3U" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="sAQAMSUx27"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-vspo-recorded-136174-simultaneous-viewers-the-largest-number-in-history/">VTuberグループ ぶ